    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A group of scripts, including book hands and documentary scripts, and formal and cursive styles, predominant in Europe from the late 12th to the 16th century, and in some areas still later.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
